IMMEDIATE
No.55/4/CF-67(i)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 5th June 1967.
The undersigned is directed to state that, with effect
from the forenoon of June 5, 1967, Shri M.S. Gurupadaswamy
relinquished the office of Minister of State in the Department
of Atomic Energy, and assumed the office of Minister of State
in the Ministry of Food, Agriculture, Community Development
and Cooperation.
(D.P. Chopra)
for Cabinet Secretary.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Prime Minister/the
Joint Secretary to the Prime Minister/the PMvate Seceetary
to the Prine Minister, for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Secretary to the Vice-President, for information,
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman,
Railway Board, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries of the Government of
India/Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat, for
information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Seeretary to the Cabinet.
250 Copies./
